The best way to reduce mosquitoes is to eliminate the places where the mosquito lays her eggs. That is to avoid the artificial water containers.

The bowl of the instant noodle and the cup of the handmade drink are also the potential risky containers.

If you want to report the water containers which may be the place for mosquito to lay eggs, just download the "mosquito man" app.

